The Vergani Cup January is a 9-round Swiss tournament taking place from 2–9 January 2022 in Cattolica, Italy.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 15 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.grandiscacchi.com
